original_title: Micke Dubois - Mycket mer än Svullo
overview: In the 80's he took the Swedish entertainment business by storm with a completely new type of humour. Cheeky, witty and gifted—the secret behind the phenomenon. He challenged the Swedish entertainment business with a phenomenal situational comedy where he gave his all.
title: Micke Dubois - A lot more than Svullo
